    "text": "Definition 2: A Context-Free Grammar (CFG) $G = ( V , \\Sigma , R , S )$ with $V$ a finite set of variables, $\\Sigma$ a finite set of terminal symbols, $R$ a finite set of rules $V \\to ( V \\cup \\Sigma ) ^ { * }$ $S$ a start variable. ",
